{
  name: "ferris",
  short: "Ferris",
  description: "Ferris Sweep — minimal 34-key col-stag split. Same col-stag splay as the Halcyon Elora v2's alpha core, but without the number row, outer-pinky column, or the outer five thumb keys per hand.",

  // Col-stag main block. Ids follow docs/id-convention.md:
