  // Ferris has no number row (no k31..k40) and no outer-pinky
  // column (no k41..k49). Alpha core only; thumbs below.
  //
  // Geometry mirrors halcyon_elora_v2's col-stag splay:
  //   pinky-outer & pinky-inner: pulled back 0.75
  //   ring:    pulled back 0.25
  //   middle:  pushed forward 0.5
  //   index-outer: pulled back 0.25
  //   index-inner: baseline
